Package org.epochx.epox.trig

Class Summary
ArcCosecantFunction A function node which performs the inverse trigonometric function of arc-cosecant, called ARCCSC.
ArcCosineFunction A function node which performs the inverse trigonometric function of arc-cosine, called ARCCOS.
ArcCotangentFunction A function node which performs the inverse trigonometric function of arc-cotangent, called ARCCOT.
ArcSecantFunction A function node which performs the inverse trigonometric function of arc-secant, called ARCSEC.
ArcSineFunction A function node which performs the inverse trigonometric function of arc-sine, called ARCSIN.
ArcTangentFunction A function node which performs the inverse trigonometric function of arc-tangent, called ARCTAN.
AreaHyperbolicCosineFunction A function node which performs the inverse hyperbolic trigonometric function of area hyperbolic cosine, called ARCOSH.
AreaHyperbolicSineFunction A function node which performs the inverse hyperbolic trigonometric function of area hyperbolic sine, called ARSINH.
AreaHyperbolicTangentFunction A function node which performs the inverse hyperbolic trigonometric function of area hyperbolic tangent, called ARTANH.
CosecantFunction A function node which performs the reciprocal trigonometric function of cosecant, called CSC.
CosineFunction A function node which performs the trigonometric function of cosine, called COS.
CotangentFunction A function node which performs the reciprocal trigonometric function of cotangent, called COT.
HyperbolicCosineFunction A function node which performs the hyperbolic trigonometric function of hyperbolic cosine, called COSH.
HyperbolicSineFunction A function node which performs the hyperbolic trigonometric function of hyperbolic sine, called SINH.
HyperbolicTangentFunction A function node which performs the hyperbolic trigonometric function of hyperbolic tangent, called TANH.
SecantFunction A function node which performs the reciprocal trigonometric function of secant, called SEC.
SineFunction A function node which performs the trigonometric function of sine.
TangentFunction A function node which performs the trigonometric function of tangent, called TAN.
